LAST-MODIFIED:20260116T004436Z
DESCRIPTION:This month we will be reading Spoon River Anthology by Edgar 
 Lee Masters.This unique classic of narrative poetry is a connecting thread
  throughout How to Read a Book\, standing out as the characters' favorite
  book club pick. We'll read it for ourselves and discuss why it plays such
  a big role in our Lincolnwood Reads novel. Registration required to rece
 ive Zoom information.
