 e will watch the Zoom interview together and reflect on this year’s Linc
 olnwood Reads title and its themes of redemption and second chances. Audie
 nce members may submit questions during the Q&A segment of the program. Pl
 ease note that this is a virtual appearance\, and the author will not be p
 resent at the library.If you would like to watch the Zoom interview from t
 he comfort of your own home\, register for the Zoom webinar here.
