DESCRIPTION:Artist and Lincolnwood resident Shirley Aberg\, who has exhibit
 ed her work all around the world\, returns to lead a workshop on painting 
 a sunrise. Choose from a variety of inspirations and let your creativity g
 uide your work. Shirley will be available for advice and tips along the wa
 y. Shirley Aberg was a school counselor for 25 years but has always dabbl
 ed in art. She painted watercolors for several years and multimedia (paste
 ls and collages). Recently\, she's begun painting with acrylic. A native o
 f Chicago\, Shirley has exhibited and sold her art in Illinois\, Florida\,
  California\, New York\, and England.
